endlegend

legend bottom
  <b>Pattern Application</b>
  |= Pattern |= Layer |= Key element |= Benefit |
  | <back:#FFF8E1><b>Pipe-and-Filter</b></back> | Layer 1 → 2 → 3 | HPF→Envelope→Detector→Calculator | Each filter independently replaceable |
  | <back:#EAF7EA><b>MVC + Observer</b></back> | Layer 3 ↔ 4 | Engine=Model(Subject) · Tabs=View(Observer) · MainWindow=Controller | Model notifies Views via measurementReady() — Observer is MVC's notification mechanism |
  | <back:#EEF6FB><b>Layered</b></back> | All layers | Forbidden cross-layer dependencies | ≤ 3-file change for new tab (AP-3) |

  |= Arrow |= Meaning |
  | ——→  Pipeline | data stream transformation (PCM → Events → Measurement) |
  | <color:#1B5E20>——→  measurementReady</color> | MVC: Model notifies Controller; Controller pushes to Views |
  | <color:#1565C0>——→  gesture</color> | MVC: Controller maps user action to Model |
  | ——|>  | implements BaseGraphTab (Passive View) |
  | - - → ❌ | violates Layered rule → breaks AP-3 ≤ 3-file target |
endlegend

@enduml
